      <title>泰国法院将于 8 月 7 日裁定是否解散反对党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/thai-court-to-rule-aug-7-whether-to-disband-opposition-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最高宪法法官将于 8 月 7 日就是否解散该国最大的反对党做出裁决，该党因发起修改严格的王室诽谤法的活动而被指控违反选举规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/thai-court-to-rule-aug-7-whether-to-disband-opposition-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 04:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 用户死亡 马来西亚严厉打击网络欺凌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/tiktok-user-s-death-sparks-malaysia-clampdown-on-cyberbullying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚 TikTok 用户的死亡促使政府考虑将网络欺凌定为犯罪，并加强互联网服务提供商的责任感。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/tiktok-user-s-death-sparks-malaysia-clampdown-on-cyberbullying</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 04:18:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国立法者将考虑额外拨款 34 亿美元用于现金赠款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/thai-lawmakers-to-weigh-extra-3-4-billion-budget-for-cash-gift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国议员于周三开始讨论总理斯雷塔·塔维辛提出的额外 1220 亿泰铢（34 亿美元）预算请求，以帮助资助政府的旗舰刺激计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/thai-lawmakers-to-weigh-extra-3-4-billion-budget-for-cash-gift</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:45:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求台湾支付防务费用后，台湾为所作所为辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/taiwan-defends-actions-after-trump-demands-it-pay-for-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普宣称芯片中心“应该为”美国保护台湾免受中国军事侵略“买单”后，台湾总理大力宣扬台湾已采取更好举措来保卫自身安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/taiwan-defends-actions-after-trump-demands-it-pay-for-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国拟对华芯片实施更严厉贸易限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-considers-tougher-trade-rules-against-companies-in-chip-crackdown-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府在对华芯片打击行动中面临阻力，该政府向盟友表示，如果东京电子有限公司 (Tokyo Electron Ltd.) 和阿斯麦控股公司 (ASML Holding NV) 等公司继续向中国提供先进的半导体技术，美国政府正在考虑采取最严厉的贸易限制措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-considers-tougher-trade-rules-against-companies-in-chip-crackdown-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 03:42:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行行长河野太郎称央行需要提高利率来提振日元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/japan-s-kono-says-central-bank-needs-to-raise-rates-to-lift-yen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本一位主管数字机构的知名大臣为竞选首相留下了空间，他呼吁央行提高利率，以提高日元汇率，降低能源和食品成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/japan-s-kono-says-central-bank-needs-to-raise-rates-to-lift-yen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 协助调查曼谷豪华酒店六起神秘死亡事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛表示，美国联邦调查局已联合泰国当局对曼谷一家豪华酒店六名外国人神秘死亡事件展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fbi-joins-probe-into-foreigner-deaths-at-bangkok-luxury-hotel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:22:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普昔日对手称赞他，展现团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/trump-s-former-rivals-unite-behind-him-at-republican-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·黑利曾称唐纳德·特朗普“完全精神错乱”且“卑微”。佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯此前曾表示，如果最“没用的共和党人”愿意“亲吻戒指”，这位前总统将拥抱他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/trump-s-former-rivals-unite-behind-him-at-republican-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 02:02:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中情局官员被指控帮助韩国购买奢侈品包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官起诉了一位前中央情报局朝鲜问题分析师，指控他离开该机构后为韩国担任间谍，以换取奢侈品和其他礼物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰国声称对阿曼什叶派清真寺发动罕见袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rare-shooting-attack-on-shiite-mosque-in-oman-leaves-six-dead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿曼称，马斯喀特一座什叶派穆斯林清真寺遭到袭击，造成 6 人死亡，这是海湾国家发生的罕见暴力事件，伊斯兰国恐怖组织后来声称对此负责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rare-shooting-attack-on-shiite-mosque-in-oman-leaves-six-dead</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
